---

## 🎯 Features

- Fully responsive design (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- Modern e-commerce UI layout
- Product cards with images and pricing
- Shopping cart UI (quantity, total, controls)
- Checkout section with receipt design
- Clean and organized code structure
- Beginner-friendly frontend project

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

This project is optimized for:
- 📱 Mobile devices (320px+)
- 📟 Tablets (600px+)
- 💻 Desktop screens (900px+)

---

## 🧠 What I Learned

- How to build responsive layouts using CSS Grid & Flexbox
- Structuring real-world frontend projects
- Creating reusable UI components
- Improving spacing, alignment, and visual hierarchy
- Building e-commerce UI logic (cart + checkout design)

---

## 📌 Future Improvements

- Add full JavaScript cart functionality (add/remove/update items)
- Connect to backend API or database
- Add authentication system (login/register)
- Improve animations and micro-interactions
- Integrate payment system UI
- Convert into full-stack e-commerce project

---

## ⚙️ How to Run This Project

1. Clone the repository  
2. Open folder in VS Code  
3. Run `index.html` in your browser  

